---
const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-neutral-200 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/60 via-white to-white dark:from-neutral-900/60 dark:via-neutral-900 dark:to-neutral-950">
  <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 px-6 py-12 md:flex-row md:justify-between">
    <div class="max-w-md space-y-4">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-accent">Fun Phone</p>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">Tu central inteligente para llamadas, contactos y productividad.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
        <span>Aplicación Android sin anuncios, diseñada para respetar tu privacidad y ayudarte a mantenerte organizado.</span>
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Descarga">
        <a
          href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bookverse.contacts"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-accent px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-accent/30 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-accent/90 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10.75 2.75a.75.75 0 00-1.5 0v6.5H4a.75.75 0 000 1.5h5.25v6.5a.75.75 0 001.5 0v-6.5H16a.75.75 0 000-1.5h-5.25v-6.5z"/></svg>
          Google Play
        </a>
        <a
          href={baseUrl + 'roadmap/'}
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/30 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-accent transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-accent hover:bg-accent/10 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 7l6 6-6 6M9 7h12"/></svg>
          Roadmap
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid flex-1 grid-cols-1 gap-8 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Sitio</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2" aria-label="Navegación secundaria">
          <li><a href={baseUrl + 'features/'} class="hover:text-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">Funciones</a></li>
          <li><a href={baseUrl + 'faq/'} class="hover:text-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">FAQ</a></li>
          <li><a href={baseUrl + 'privacy/'} class="hover:text-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">Privacidad</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://bookverse.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">Bookverse</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Soporte</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="mailto:santiago.moncada.dev@gmail.com" class="hover:text-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">Contacto directo</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bookverse.contacts&hl=es&gl=US" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">Calificar en Play Store</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/113410" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-accent focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">Reembolsos y ayuda</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-neutral-200 bg-white/70 py-6 text-center text-xs text-neutral-500 backdrop-blur dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-950/60 dark:text-neutral-400">
    &copy; {currentYear} Fun Phone · Bookverse. Todos los derechos reservados.
  </div>
</footer>
